I thought I was pretty knowledgeable in Onshape, but I’m stumped.

Even though I gave a teammate Editing rights to my document he can view only. When he does the same, I can edit his Onshape files. Why?

We’re both using the Onshape Student license.

Thanks, we tried that. But we found the problem.

One of our members signed up for a Free account instead of a Student account. Free account users can’t edit other people’s documents, even with editing permission.
